bedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://jalopnik.com/the-best-corvette-is-a-cheap-corvette-1851530601\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://jalopnik.com/the-best-corvette-is-a-cheap-corvette-1851530601\"\u003ethe Corvette\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e. Not every American automobile has such pedigree, however.  - Owen Bellwood \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://jalopnik.com/what-s-the-worst-american-car-ever-made-1851675899\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://jalopnik.com/what-s-the-worst-american-car-ever-made-1851675899\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
